parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The separation of the firewall from the floor boards can allow exhaust gases from the generator to enter the motorhome, potentially causing carbon monoxide poisoning or other health hazards.
symptoms: Gap between the floor board and firewall mounting
horizontal and vertical separation of the firewall from the floor boards
diesel exhaust fumes can be smelled inside the motorhome when the generator is running.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The structural failure of the motorhome chassis can lead to separation of critical components, such as the firewall, and compromise the safety and integrity of the vehicle.

horizontal and vertical separation of critical components.
